tourBios.carHigh: 2015: Finished T2 at Florida Qualifying Tournament, with rounds of 65-68-68-65...Puncuated regulation play with a 12-under 276 and a final-hole eagle to move into a five-way playoff at the PC Financial Open. Parred the first playoff hole, falling to match birdie putts by Drew Weaver and Adam Svensson. Earned a T2 finish.
tourBios.personal: Went to Walsh Jesuit High School...Hopes to play St. Andrews some day...Dream foursome would include his parents and Arnold Palmer...Big Manchester United fan.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA T was T2nd in 2015 at the PC Financial Open.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks T74th in Scoring Average (Actual) on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA TOUR Canada.
